about:
Welcome to the RPM European GT3 Series. 
 
 We are not looking to reinvent the wheel here we are just looking to provide clean fair racing for like minded people no matter which end of the field you find yourself. 
 
 For more details or to join head to our discord - https://discord.gg/ha3VuNVXNn
